  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large saucepan over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the beef and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the onions, garlic, and ginger and cook until the onions are translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the cumin, coriander, paprika, salt, and pepper and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the tomatoes, saffron, and its soaking liquid and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 20 minutes, or until the beef is tender.",
    "Stir in the chopped parsley and serve hot, garnished with additional parsley if desired."
